Ilchakenini oare


1   Naaitokini aaisho entemet naikununo anaa eng'udi, naajokini nanu, “Inyo tetema enkaji e Enkai o ewueji o lperere lo lasar o lelo ooserem te ine. 
2   Kake mitem ake olgoriet otii boo e nkaji e Enkai. Tapala ilo amu eishooki iloreren, naa keituny ninche ina ang sinyati too lapaitin artam o aare. 
3  Naa kaisho ilchakenini laainei oare engolon naibonishore nkolong'i enkalifu nabo o iip are o ntomoni ile, eishopito ilkuniyiani.”


4   Kulo ninche lelo oirienito aare, o lelo kilang'ilang'eta aare ooitashe te dukuya Olaitoriani le nkop. 
5  Naa te neyieu oltung'ani neinyal ninche, nepuku enkima too nkutukie enye, nemut ilmang'ati lenye. Te neyieu oltung'ani near ninche neari metua aaiko neijia. 
6   Eeta ninche engolon naikenie oloing'ang'e pee meshau enchan te nena olong'i e naibon enye. Neeta ninche engolon naitoreyie nkariak o enaibelekenyie metaa osarge. Near enkop to lmeitai ake pooki naaba anaa enayieu ninche. 
7   Ore ake pee eidip ninche enchakenisho enye, ore ina ng'ues nailepua te ina gumoto nemeeta eneiting'ie nedumaki ninche enjore, nemir ninche, near ninche metuata. 
8   Neirrag impopoki enye te nkoitoi nalala eina anasa kitok, naji te nkiroroto e nkitumususet, Sodom o Misiri, naa te ine apa etashoki Olaitoriani lenye. 
9  Ore too nkolong'i uni o lpisiai ore iltung'ana loo loshon, o lng'ejepa o loreren neshil nena popoki enye, nemit enukari aapik inkuraren. 
10  Ore lelo olomanya enkop, neshipakino ninche, neitayu isiruai neishoro nkishorot, amu ore kulo oibonok le Enkai pokira aare, naisomita oleng lelo ootii enkop. 
11   Kake ore te siadi nena olong'i uni o lpisiai, nejing enkiyang'et e nkishui naing'uaa Enkai, atua ninche neitashe ninche too nkejek enye, neiput enkuretisho sapuk lelo ootoduaa ninche. 
12   Ore ina kata nening oltoilo sapuk oing'uaa shumata ejoki ninche. “Elepu wootu ene!” Ore eing'orita ilmang'ati lenye neilep ninche aapuo shumata te nkatampoi. 
13   Ore te ina saa nejing olokirikiri kitok enkop, neurori ematua e tomon e ina anasa. Neari iltung'ana nkalifuni naapishana, metuata te ina kikirikirata. Neiputukuny lelo ootelekutua, neisho enkisisa Enkai e shumata.


14  Etulusoyie entaboi e are. Ng'ura, kelotu entaboi e uni asioku.

Entarumpeta e naapishana


15   Neitoki olmalaika li oopishana aosh entarumpeta enye, netii iltoiloishi sapuki shumata oojo, “Etaa enkitoo e nkop enkitoo o Laitoriani lang o ene Kristo lenye, naa keitoreisho ninye intarasi o ntarasi.” 
16  Ore lelo payiani tikitam o oong'uan ootoni too lorikan lenye le nkitoo te dukuya Enkai nebatata too nkomomi enye aaserem Enkai. 
17  Nejo, “Kincho iyie enashe, Olaitoriani Enkai, olopeny enkidimata pooki, otii taata, netii apa amu iwa te ngolon ino sapuk, ninterua aitoreisho. 
18   Etoopishote loreren, kake neewuo engoro ino, neewuo enkata naiguanareki ilootuata, nilaaki ole koisiaayio isinkan linono, iloibonok sinyat o lelo ooure enkarna ino, ilooti o lkituaak, o enkata namuti lelo amutak le nkop.” 
19   Neitokini aabol enkaji e Enkai te shumata nedoli osanduku lo sotua lenye ti atua enkaji e Enkai. Netii enkimerlel oo nkiwuang'at o ltoiloishi oobuak, o ndarat e nkikurrukur o lokirikiri le nkop, o enchan oo soito sapuki oleng.

